   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>The design is done, I'd say. I updated the wiki page to reflect the plan.

I'm testing it out by doing a backup. Once a successful backup is completed, and
two days passes with no comments on the backup plan or this bug, I'll consider
the backup plan to be fuly "Designed".</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
   <th><a href="msg2909">msg2909 (view)</a></th>
