  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>This includes:
1. looking into OSU OSL's existing backup policies
2. determining a good long-term host for storing backups (taking into account OSU OSL)
3. designing a backup plan for the OpenHatch data, including the database, config files, and code
4. presenting the plan to devel and getting buy-in</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
